<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/nav%3Aside/interwikiFrame.html?category=_default&amp;pagename=http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5270" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="" style=""></iframe></p>
